{"tid":2487191,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"初戀既影響真係咁大？","createTime":"2021-04-13T11:26:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-13T11:34:24.000Z","uid":345698,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0c833872b90c1aa46ab98ed7e23642ce89f11043","tid":2487191,"uid":345698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:26:18.000Z","msg":"成日都凝住凝住覺得對方心入面仲有佢初戀<br />\n每次一諗到呢到就覺得好痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似無論自己幾努力/幾愛佢都好 <br />\n都冇辦法做到佢心入面既第一位<br />\n<br />\n我自己黎講完全唔覺得初戀地位必然&gt;&gt;任何一任<br />\n對佢付出幾多可能都不及佢初戀既一句說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我明白有時候留戀既可能只係段回憶同青春<br />\n而唔係個個人<br />\n但都好唔鐘意呢種感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加上佢上一個好似hurt得佢幾深 <br />\n搞到我硬係覺得佢冇辦法完全信任我 同毫無保留地愛我<br />\n<br />\n到底我可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d77726eaa11c97716017961f6aae941fb11f12f3","tid":2487191,"uid":9392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:27:08.000Z","msg":"哈 又一pair準備分手 開心~"},{"pid":"d5c870dd857b1a70df3ab039d1d74d55e6ba3a40","tid":2487191,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:31:06.000Z","msg":"多餘 有得你屌就屌啦"},{"pid":"3c6bf16b1c10d0c45c692c06ff514cde32c759e5","tid":2487191,"uid":302354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:31:45.000Z","msg":"我都覺得自己已經做唔到毫無保留咁對下一個<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d63f0f761df614e17187caf364f1fa9864e7ed42","tid":2487191,"uid":328876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:34:24.000Z","msg":"比時間同耐性<br />\n用行動話比佢聽佢係可以信你"}]}